                          Chunk - 16KiB
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| C0[] | (Padding) | C1[] | (Padding) | C2[] | (Padding) | ... |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|

Example:
C0 = 16B
C1 = 8B
C2 = 4B

= 28B per Entity

No alignment

Entities:
16.384 % 28 = 4
16.384 / 28 = 585
= 585 Entities, 4B wasted

C0: 16 * 585 = 9360
C1: 8 * 585 = 4680
C2: 4 * 585 = 2340

|--------------------------------------------|
| C0[] | (Padding) | C1[] | (Padding) | C2[] |
|--------------------------------------------|
^------^-----------^------^-----------^------^
   |        0          |        0        |
  0-9360           9360-14040       14040-16380
  

Example:
C0 = 16B
C1 = 8B
C2 = 4B

= 28B per Entity

32B alignment (for AVX2)

C0 -> count is multiple of 2 or padding of 16B
C1 -> count is multiple of 4 or padding of 8B/16B/24B
C2 -> count is multiple of 8 or padding of 4B/8B/12B/16B/20B/24B/28B

Entity Count N:
16.384 / 28 = 585

Sizes Si:
S0 = N * 16 = 9360
S1 = N * 8  = 4680
S2 = N * 4  = 2340

Alignment Ai:
A0 = 32
A1 = 32
A2 = 32

Offset o = 0
Position Pi
Padding PAi

PA0 = 0
P0 = 0
o += 9360 // o = 9360

PA1 = 9360 % 32 = 16
o += PA1 // o = 9276
P1 = o = 9376

EntityCount N;
Component0Size CS0
Component1Size CS1
HeaderSize HS (fixed, e.g. 32B)
|---------------------------------------------------------|
| HS | ID x N | (Padding) | CS0 x N | (Padding) | CS1 x N |
|---------------------------------------------------------|
